fullTextAnnotation.text:
Sides
Please let us know if you would like any
of the sides served first.
Add a side of liquid cheese to any side
or meal $2.9
Pulled Pork Loaded Chips
Battered chips topped with pulled pork,
sweet onion bbq sauce & melted cheese
garnished with crispy coleslaw.
Pork & Veal Arancini Balls
Arborio rice mixed with pork & veal bolognese
sauce & cheese coated in breadcrumbs then
lightly fried garnished with napoli sauce,
parmesan cheese, aioli & parsley.
Chicken Wings
Your choice of spicy OR honey BBQ sauce.
GF
Nachos
Corn chips topped with pork & veal bolognese sauce,
jalapeño peppers, melted cheese, guacamole
& sour cream. Can be made vegetarian if asked.
Lemon Pepper Calamari
Tender calamari strips lightly dressed with salt
& lemon pepper flour then fried & served with
lemon & aioli dipping sauce.
Bowl of Wedges
Served with sour cream & sweet chilli.
Bowl of Chips
Served with tomato sauce.
V
Kids
Includes complimentary pancake at dinner

Chicken Nuggets & Chips
